{"type": "article", "id": 13384, "title": "简洁水压秤", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-12T07:13:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000248MBmCOiqD2XtY4ocr.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tTroy Turner 设计了一款超级便携式的秤，它利用水受到压力变形的的特点，像一个暖水袋那样，装上水就可以轻松得到物体的重量。当不使用时，把水放干就可以把秤折起来收纳，外形简单时尚，轻松便携。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141203vuHdY0AOikxCmly4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141203CxioTuwPH05caOKV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141204698E01VCrKGwsmMc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141204d2NAb3ZyEJeDRTFm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141205FtG6ioZAL9xrMECT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141205hzPISX0t8vs9LNDH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}